      "Use Canadian and public-facing style guidance for clarity, accessibility, and audience-sensitive wording.",
      "Do not embed copyrighted textbook chapters verbatim.",
      "Store bibliographic detail and use-case notes so Nyx and Marion can cite and prioritize sources intelligently."
    ]
